title: Clearance Heights - Bridges and Underpasses
description:
A. SUMMARY 
Location and clearance heights for underpasses throughout San Francisco.

B. METHODOLOGY  
Manual updates

C. UPDATE FREQUENCY  
Once or twice per year. 

D. OTHER CRITICAL INFO  
None
